{"tid":893113,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯舊友:牙朗曾在曼聯被群嘲","createTime":"2018-11-07T11:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T16:39:23.000Z","uid":25345,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b685df66b57aede18631dfb7c73486c89810c979","tid":893113,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newc/20150129/photo/0129-00574-004b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fnewc%2F20150129%2Fphoto%2F0129-00574-004b1.jpg&h=8fc97338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明天凌晨，尤文將在主場再戰曼聯，牙朗又將再次面對老東家。在接受天空體育采訪時，曼聯舊將費查透露牙朗曾經在球隊中被嘲笑過，但葡萄牙人最終用實際表現征服了隊友們。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;在加盟曼聯時，牙朗就堅信自己會成為世界上最好的球員，他把訓練提升到了另一個境界。&rdquo;費查說道，&ldquo;剛開始時，大家都會有這種雄心壯志，但只有牙朗日復一日的堅持了下來。說起來容易，做起來可太難了。有時候，他會在腳踝上綁上沙袋進行快速衝刺。有隊友們會嘲笑他，但他並不在乎，也沒有就此停下腳步。最終，他贏得了大家的尊重，大家都欣賞他的進取心。有些隊友會對牙朗開一些不帶惡意的玩笑，但在內心深處，我們都尊重他想要成為世界最佳的渴望和決心。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9fe1b77b1bc4c657b9f7a1e287a95956870cdd4e","tid":893113,"uid":2607,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"講鬥志同爭勝心真係同kobe同級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b1658fa86421d97d0e1848882d2a89bc0a7eb3","tid":893113,"uid":155815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"回家吧牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84287da301a361e1e1dbb89332c8e73e9869dcfa","tid":893113,"uid":192158,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1be98f4a7a2de561d8b99f12a203495b423a2ba","tid":893113,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9fe1b77b1bc4c657b9f7a1e287a95956870cdd4e","tid":893113,"uid":2607,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-0